WEBVTT

00:00.130 --> 00:02.300
I gave Dad a Japanese signature.

00:02.620 --> 00:05.010
Do difficult kanji suit him well?

00:05.650 --> 00:11.570
Just a voice with a text is boring, so I set up the computer so that I can see an image of Dad and have him talk.

00:12.220 --> 00:14.800
I guess there are limitations.

00:15.200 --> 00:21.370
I programmed the routing devices so that Dad can communicate with the Net and receive feedback.

00:21.900 --> 00:26.130
Dad is studying the Net now, so he’ll know more dirty words than me.

00:26.360 --> 00:27.890
You’re a dirty old man, Dad!
